{"tid":572574,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GiGi 學 城 城 捐 歌 迷 利 是","createTime":"2018-02-25T16:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T20:23:47.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"26fd5d83e0a0c347a322cce9d19a43fb9195ea7b","tid":572574,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T16:28:47.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（GiGi）日前在銅鑼灣時代廣場UA Cine Times舉辦梁詠琪粉絲場，GiGi邀請了過百名粉絲入場一起欣賞《西遊記女兒國》，GiGi飾演的國師，是出自荷李活的特效化妝，每日開工需要5個小時化妝，收工要花一小時落妝。GiGi對現場的粉絲說：「雖然我喺戲裏面嘅髮線好高，但我個額頭唔係天生咁高，係化妝效果！」惹來哄堂大笑。<br />\n<br />\n農曆新年，粉絲群起要求GiGi派利是，她說：「講真㗎！頭先佢哋問得我太突然啦！我又冇帶利是喺身。」GiGi指每年會將愛女Sofia的利是錢捐到慈善機構，今次未有預備利是給影迷，所以她決定效法郭富城，以全香港人名義捐款當派利是的做法，以歌迷之名捐錢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180224/large/24ec2p20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180224%2Flarge%2F24ec2p20.jpg&h=d3a834f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f0d3efd001f86dafcc371f2a8cf26bd77e915b4","tid":572574,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T16:32:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3565066d6829413fac8e783f3f4cbf0695a8e56b","tid":572574,"uid":188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T16:46:01.000Z","msg":"有無捐出西班牙新鮮精液"},{"pid":"96899df57423d343e854e43db5aa16d3f9de8bc6","tid":572574,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T16:50:44.000Z","msg":"呼籲gigi 將佢老公既西班牙新鮮精液捐比樓上既無敵神駒巴打，佢好需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e102c8db3e47248bc99039424ecad0f4e2aef16d","tid":572574,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T19:50:03.000Z","msg":"Sergio.gif"},{"pid":"521fda704112b4cdc5cc298fd2e008ba9498b3eb"